    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-olive-tapenade-ragu-with-fresh-tagliatelle/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Chop your <strong>'Nduja</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-olive-tapenade-ragu-with-fresh-tagliatelle/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>'Nduja </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan with the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until very fragrant</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-olive-tapenade-ragu-with-fresh-tagliatelle/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>fresh</strong> <strong>tagliatelle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the tagliatelle for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the tagliatelle, reserving 175ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[230ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-olive-tapenade-ragu-with-fresh-tagliatelle/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the 'Nduja is very fragrant, reduce the heat to medium and add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>soft cheese </strong>and <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>with the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water </strong>and mix it all together with a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Increase the heat to high and cook for 1-2 min or until thickened</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-olive-tapenade-ragu-with-fresh-tagliatelle/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, add the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>tagliatelle </strong>with your <strong>black & green olive tapenade </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>spicy 'Nduja & olive tapenade rag\u00f9 with fresh tagliatelle</strong></p><p>Set aside with the lid on for 1-2 min for the flavours to develop</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-olive-tapenade-ragu-with-fresh-tagliatelle/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine a little <strong>olive oil </strong>and your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>salad </strong>and toss \u2013 this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-olive-tapenade-ragu-with-fresh-tagliatelle/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy 'Nduja & olive tapenade rag\u00f9 with fresh tagliatelle</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining grated Italian cheese </strong>and a grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> balsamic salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
